quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  35,19,"Bum…óo e ji'oowo potataa,"
  35,20,"wonaa ni…ďe …óen e ndaygu ngun,"
  35,21,"wonaa …óowdi ndi e henndu wulndu ndu."
  35,22,"Wonaa kadi wuur…ďe …ďen potata e maay…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla no nanina on mo o muuyani. Wanaa an [Nulaa…óo], woni naninoowo, won…ďe ka genaale …ďeen."
  35,23,"Aan a wonaani, si wonaa jerrtinoowo."
  35,24,"Pellet, Min nulirii ma goonga, ko a beltinoowo e jeertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wonaa jerrtinoowo fe∆ī∆īii e ma…ď…ďe."
  35,25,"Si …ďe njeddii ma, hari adinoo…ďe …ďe …ďen njedduno (Nulaa…ďe mum), feewndo …ďen Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe ngaddannoo …ďanngannduyeeji, e ∆äeri e feftere ndayginoore."
  35,26,"Refti nanngitir mi yeddu…ďe …ďen (halakuyee). Tesko no lepte am …óen mba…ótinirnoo."
  35,27,"E a yiaani won'de Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Min pu…óiniri …óam dim…óe ceertu…óe noone. Hino ka pelle, …óate daneeje e bo…óeeje ceertyu…óe noone, e pete …ďaleeje."
  35,28,"Hino e yim…ďe …ďen, e daabeeji …óin, e neemoraa…ói …óin, …ói nooneeji mum kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko kulata Alla e jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen, ko anndu…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla ko poolu…óo, kaforoowo."
  35,29,"∆Āeen janngoo…ďe deftere Alla nden, …ďe √Īii…ďi e Juulde, …ďe nafqii ko Min arsiki …ďe kon gunndoo e kene, he…ďe njoortii njulaaku ngu sontataa."
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana …ďe njo…ďdiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, o …ďeyda …ďe e …ďural makko ngal. KaŇčko, ko o kaforoowo, gannditanoowo [on] ."